{
  "Infinite Geometric Series": "无限几何系列",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is 0.999... as a fraction?": "什么是0.999... 作为分数?",
  "0.999... = 9/10 + 9/100 + ... = (9/10)/(1 − 1/10) = (9/10)/(9/10) = 1 exactly.": "0.999 = 9/10+9/100+...= (9/10)/(1 - 1/10)= (9/10)/(9/10)/(9/10)= 1 准确。",
  "What is the condition for convergence of an infinite geometric series?": "无限几何序列的趋同条件是什么?",
  "An infinite geometric series converges if and only if the absolute value of the common ratio is less than 1: |r| < 1.": "如果而且只有在共同比率的绝对值低于1时,一个无限的几何序列会趋同: < 1时。",
  "What is the formula for the sum of an infinite geometric series when |r| < 1?": "当 < 1 \" 时, 无限几何序列的总和的公式是什么?",
  "When |r| < 1, the infinite geometric series sums to S = a₁/(1 − r). The finite formula Sₙ = a₁(1 − rⁿ)/(1 − r) approaches this as n → ∞ since rⁿ → 0.": "当 < r < 1 时, 无限几何序列数数数为 S = a1/ (1) - r. Sn = a1(1 - rn) / (1 - r) / (1 - r) 将之作为n  * * * * = a1/ (1 - r) / (1 - r) = 0 。",
  "What is the meaning of 'partial sum' in the context of an infinite series?": "“部分总和”在无限系列中的含义是什么?",
  "A partial sum Sₙ is the sum of only the first n terms. As n increases, partial sums approximate the infinite sum more closely.": "Sn部分总和只是第一个n条件的总和。作为n增加,部分总和接近无限总和。",
  "What is the meaning of 'infinite series'?": "\"无限系列\"是什么意思?",
  "An infinite series has infinitely many terms. Its value is defined as the limit of its partial sums, if that limit exists.": "无限系列有无限多的术语。 如果存在部分总和,其价值被定义为其部分总和的限度。",
  "A bouncing ball is dropped from 10 meters and reaches 60% of its previous height on each bounce. What is the total distance the ball travels (up and down combined)?": "弹跳球从10米处投下,每弹跳时的高度达到前一个高度的60%。球的总距离(上下总和)是多少?",
  "Down = 10, Up+Down bounces = 2 · Σ (10 · 0.6ⁿ) for n=1 to ∞ = 2 · 10(0.6)/(1−0.6) = 2 · 15 = 30. Total = 10 + 30 = 40 m.": "向下=10,向上+向下反弹=2 □ □ (10 □ 0.6n),n=1至=2 □ 10(0.6)/(1-0.6)=2 □ 15 =30 =30 总计=10 + 30 = 40米。",
  "A pendulum swings 20 cm on its first swing and each subsequent swing is 90% of the previous one. What is the total distance the pendulum swings before stopping?": "钟摆在第一次秋千上摆20厘米,其后每次秋千是前一次秋千的90%。 钟摆在停下来前的总距离是多少?",
  "S = a₁/(1 − r) = 20/(1 − 0.9) = 20/0.1 = 200 cm.": "S = a1/(1 - r) = 20/(1 - 0.9) = 20/0.1 = 200厘米。",
  "A government stimulus gives $1,000 to each citizen. Each person spends 80% of what they receive, and those recipients also spend 80%, and so on. What is the total economic impact (spending) of the stimulus?": "政府刺激政策为每个公民提供1 000美元。 每个人花费其所得的80%,而领取者也花费80%,等等。 刺激措施的总体经济影响(支出)是什么?",
  "First spending = $800, then $640, $512, ... This is a geometric series with a₁ = 800, r = 0.8. Total spending = 800/(1 − 0.8) = 800/0.2 = $4,000.": "第一个支出=800美元,然后是640美元,512美元.这是一个几何序列,a1=800,r=0.8,总支出=800/(1-0.8)=800/0.2=4 000美元。",
  "A drug has a half-life such that 50% remains after each dose interval. If 100 mg is taken repeatedly at each interval, what is the long-run steady-state amount in the body?": "一种药物的半衰期为50%,在每次剂量间隔后还剩下50%。如果每间隔一次重复服用100毫克,体内的长期稳定状态值是多少?",
  "At steady state, the amount right after a dose is S = 100/(1 − 0.5) = 100/0.5 = 200 mg.": "在稳定状态下,剂量后右转剂量为S=100/(1-0.5)=100/0.5=200毫克。",
  "A fractal pattern starts with a triangle of area 1. At each step, the total shaded area is multiplied by 3/4. What is the total shaded area after infinitely many steps?": "分形图案从区域1的三角形开始。每一步,总阴影区乘以3/4。在无穷无尽的多个步骤之后,总阴影区是多少?",
  "S = 1/(1 − 3/4) = 1/(1/4) = 4.": "S = 1/(1-1- 3/4) = 1/(1/4) = 4。",
  "A forest loses 10% of its deer population each year due to migration. If 200 new deer are born each year, what is the long-run stable population?": "如果每年有200头新鹿出生,那么长期稳定的人口是多少?",
  "At equilibrium, births = losses: 200 = 0.10 · P → P = 2,000. Equivalently, the sum 200 + 200(0.9) + 200(0.9)² + ... = 200/(1 − 0.9) = 2,000.": "在平衡时,出生=损失:200 = 0.10 P = 2,000 P = P = P = 2,000 等值,200 + 200 (0.9) + 200 (0.9) +... = 200 (1) = 0.9) = 2 000。",
  "An oil spill spreads in concentric rings. The first ring has area 100 m² and each subsequent ring has area equal to 1/2 the previous ring. What is the total area the spill eventually covers?": "第一枚环有100平方米面积,其后每枚环有面积等于前一枚环的1/2。溢漏最终覆盖的总面积是多少?",
  "S = 100/(1 − 1/2) = 100/0.5 = 200 m².": "S = 100/(1-1-1/2) = 100/0.5 = 200平方米。",
  "A machine operates at full power, then at 70% power, then at 49% power, and so on. If full power produces 500 units, what is the total output over its entire lifetime?": "一台机器在全功率下运行,然后是70%的功率,然后是49%的功率,等等。 如果全功率产生500个单位,那么其整个生命周期的总产出是多少?",
  "r = 0.7. S = 500/(1 − 0.7) = 500/0.3 ≈ 1,666.67 ≈ 1,667 units.": "r = 0.7 S = 500/(1 = 0.7) = 500/0.3 = 1 666.67 = 1 667 个单元。",
  "A company donates $5,000. Each recipient organization passes 40% of what they receive to another organization. What is the total amount all organizations receive combined?": "一家公司捐助5 000美元,每个接受组织将所得的40%分给另一个组织,所有组织收到的总额加起来是多少?",
  "Total = 5000 + 5000(0.4) + 5000(0.4)² + ... = 5000/(1 − 0.4) = 5000/0.6 ≈ $8,333.": "总计=5000+5000(0.4)+5000(0.4)2+...=5000(1)-0.4)=5000/0.6+8,333美元。"
}